Requirements:The qualified candidate will have a Bachelor's degree and five years of relevant experience. Financial analysis, budgeting, forecasting and financial reporting experience is required. Nonprofit accounting experience is a plus. Advanced Excel skills and experience with complex financial budget models are required, as well as familiarity with Sage Intaact or another cloud-based accounting system. A logical thought process and good analytical and organizational skills are required. Because this is a hands-on position that works closely with all departments in the organization, the successful candidate will be highly motivated and exhibit a positive attitude and a willingness to go “above and beyond” in dealings with fellow employees.

